description: Aaliyah the supermodel/popstar has had a bit of a stalker situation on her hand. Some creepy guy named Brick won’t stop liking, commenting, and messaging her on all of her social media accounts. She wouldn’t mind a little attention, but this dude has definitely been crossing the line. One day Aaliyah receives a strange call from a man whispering very odd and scary things to her. Her heart begins to beat faster. Just as she walks into her room, she gets blindsided by someone. What happens next? Well wouldn’t you like to know….
title: Social Media Creeper
